calls.command:
claude -p You are the model backend for an Atomic Agents bakeoff.

Return only a JSON object. No prose. No markdown fences.

Conversation messages:

[
  {
    "role": "system",
    "content": "# IDENTITY and PURPOSE\n- You are a deterministic bakeoff summarizer.\n\n# INTERNAL ASSISTANT STEPS\n- Return exactly {\"summary\":\"tool artifact created\",\"ok\":true}.\n- Return exactly the requested structured JSON.\n\n# OUTPUT INSTRUCTIONS\n- Always respond using the proper JSON schema.\n- Always use the available additional information and context to enhance the response."
  },
  {
    "role": "user",
    "content": "{\"tool_result\":\"bakeoff-tool-ok\"}"
  }
]

Required JSON schema:

{
  "description": "Output from the bakeoff summarizer agent.",
  "properties": {
    "summary": {
      "description": "Summary",
      "title": "Summary",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "ok": {
      "description": "Whether summarization succeeded",
      "title": "Ok",
      "type": "boolean"
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "summary",
    "ok"
  ],
  "title": "SummarizerOutput",
  "type": "object"
} --output-format json

